members.name: weightUnit
members.doc:
The unit in which the order's weight is
 measured. Either `"KG"` or `"LB"`.

members.name: buyerNote
members.doc: A note added by the buyer.

members.name: cartId
members.doc: Unique identifier of the shopping cart.

members.name: fulfillmentStatus
members.doc:
The current fulfillment status of the order (whether the order has been delivered/collected).
One of:

 + `"NOT_FULFILLED"`: The order has not yet fulfilled.
 + `"FULFILLED"`: The order has fulfilled successfully.
 + `"CANCELLED"`: The order has been cancelled.
 + `"PARTIALLY_FULFILLED"`: The order as been partially fulfilled.

members.name: archived
members.doc: Whether or not the order has been archived.

members.name: activities
members.doc: Log of changes that were made to the order.

members.name: paymentStatus
members.doc:
The current status of the payment.
One of:

 + `"PENDING"`: The payment has not yet completed.
 + `"NOT_PAID"`: The payment has not been made.
 + `"PAID"`: The order has been paid for successfully.
 + `"PARTIALLY_REFUNDED"`: The order has been partially refunded.
 + `"FULLY_REFUNDED"`: The order has been refunded in full.
